			<section>
				<h2 id="homies">My Homies</h2>
				<p>Man, I love the long tail. There is so much interesting stuff on the web theses days, including on YouTube, wouldn&apos;t you agree? On this page I wanted to let you know about some of the people who I follow. I can&apos;t list everyone who I follow on YouTube, so the criteria for this list is whether I sponsor them on Patreon or not. Yes, I do sponsor people on Patreon! 
					<a class="external" target="_blank" rel="noopener follow" href="https://www.patreon.com/JohnElliotV" title="Click here to see my generous supporters on Patreon, and maybe join them?">Don&apos;t you?</a> :)</p>
